    "summary": "About the Agency & Syndication Desk:\nThe Agency & Syndication Desk has its focus on clubdeals and syndicated facilities. In these deals, multiple Lenders provide finance to a Company. Deals can include Commercial Finance (Factoring) and Leasing, but also Loans, Revolving Credit and other facilities.\nOur objective is twofold. As Agent, we are the central point of contact between the Company and its Lenders. This relates to information sharing, security and borrowing base management, payments, etc. Periodical information (financials, compliance certificates) and ad hoc information (waivers, amendments) are shared via the \u2018Debtdomain\u2019 platform, that provides a secured website for each deal.\nSecondly, with our Syndication activities, we help our clients to select a suitable group of Lenders. This can either be done as an \u2018underwrite\u2019 (ABN AMRO ABF providing certainty of funds), or on a \u2018best-efforts' basis.\n\nAbout ABN AMRO Asset Based Finance:\nOur ambition is to become the industry's most dynamic, regarded and renowned Asset Based Finance company, with our success firmly rooted in the success of our clients. We are a leading cross-border Asset Based Lender with over 45 years of experience. To clients located in the northwestern European region, we offer a range of services, all designed to improve business cash flows and efficiency. Asset Based Lending grows and adapts with your portfolio, unlocking funds tied up in your receivables, inventory, machinery and equipment. Consequently, it can improve your capital structure, facilitate growth, seasonal fluctuations and acquisitions and it can optimize your balance sheet ratios (off-balance).\n\nOur Asset Base Finance Solutions include:\n- Full Cross-Border Commercial Finance, where assets can be cross-collateralised and are centrally managed. Funding is maximised by leveraging your Group strength. We can establish one Group facility under a single legal agreement, funded through a lead agent structure that lends directly to your organisation. Simple and highly versatile. \n- Multi-Local Commercial Finance, which is a variation to full Cross-Border Finance. With this option we oversee all regional agreements to operate as a single joined up partner, giving autonomy to your local management teams. \n- Financial Lease (on-balance) and Operational Lease (off-balance, depending on reporting standards, e.g. IFRS).\n- Each solutions can be structured as \u2018Green loan\u2019, or \u2018Sustainable-linked facility\u2019, adding to your green strategy. Our team of experienced ESG specialists are happy to advise you on this.",
